- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of a predictive cross-modal criterion, which is a machine learning technique. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possibility as the paper uses a self-supervision technique, which is a common AI technique. 
- cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a sub-category of cs.CV and is also a possibility as the paper deals with computer vision and image processing.
